<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3367007>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lucihormetica yasuniana Vidlička, sp. n. Holotype—habitus, ♂. A, B—habitus, dorsal (A) and ventral (B) view (without the tip of abdomen); C—left hind wing. Photos A & B taken by Roman Hergovits." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3367007/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3367009>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Lucihormetica yasuniana Vidlička, sp. n. Holotype—abdomen, ♂. A—dorsal view, B—ventral view; C—T8, T9 and supra-anal plate with cerci (dorsal view); D—subgenital plate (ventral view); E—right cercus (ventral view); F, G—left (F) and right (G) styli (ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3367009/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3367011>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Lucihormetica yasuniana Vidlička, sp. n. Holotype—genitalia, ♂. A, B—ventral view, sheathed hook (A) and protruded hook (B); C, D—preputial spines, dorsal (C) and ventral (D) view, on D with part of L2d-sclerite [L2' on via]; Ehook R2 [L3']; F—cleft sclerite L1 [R3' and R4']." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3367011/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

